### Use Brackets to Edit Project 2
* Edit the source code in "bacs350/project/index.php"


### Setup Filezilla
* Run Filezilla 
* Configure New Site using Site Manager
* Connect to Bluehost with credentials (host, user, password)
* Set up youe directory paths to connect to the right place
* Send files to Bluehost


### Repeat Until Done
* Test your page at "bacs350/project/02/index.php"
* Modify the code until it looks right
* Push code every minute


### Commit changes when this works



## Step 3 - Build Brain App

### Create Home Page
* Build the page to look like [Unco-Bacs.org](https://unco-bacs.org/bacs350)
* Create your home page at "bacs350/index.php"

### Build Demo Pages
* Create pages to show class demo
    * bacs350/demo/index.php
    * Build folders: 01, 02, 03, 04, 05

### Build Project Pages
* Create pages to show class demo
    * bacs350/project/index.php
    * Build folders: 01, 02

### Build Design Patterns Pages
* Create pages to show class demo
    * bacs350/pattern/index.php
    * Build folders: 01, 02, 03, 04



## Requirements
The completed assignment must meet the following requirements.

* Page exists at "bacs350/index.php"
* Page exists at "bacs350/project/02/index.php"
* Page exists at "bacs350/demo/05/index.php"
* Page exists at "bacs350/pattern/render_page/index.php"
* Home page has custom content
* Demo page has custom content
* Project page has custom content
* Pattern page has custom content
* Github repo is shown as link on "bacs350/project/02/index.php"
* Your custom photo


